If it could be carried away from her... because of her ...

336
00:20:32,670 --> 00:20:33,720
不是吧
Oh, dear.

337
00:20:42,150 --> 00:20:44,690
就是这样 不 不 不 继续往那边
That's it. No, no, no, keep going.

338
00:20:44,910 --> 00:20:46,620
往中间一点 就是那儿
More into the center. Left in there.

339
00:20:48,150 --> 00:20:49,400
再往前点
Further.

340
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:51,430
抱歉 姑娘
Sorry, old girl.

341
00:20:52,350 --> 00:20:55,830
蜜儿 我还以为你不喜欢这种事呢
Oh, Mil! I thought you didn't approve of such things.

342
00:20:56,070 --> 00:20:57,902
万事都有头一回嘛
Try anything once.

343
00:20:57,903 --> 00:20:58,819
大概吧
I bet.

344
00:20:58,830 --> 00:21:02,130
克里斯提安 我希望你能留下来看彩排
Christian, I hope you'll stay for the dress rehearsal.

345
00:21:02,140 --> 00:21:04,050
我有点累了
I'm a little weary.

346
00:21:04,610 --> 00:21:09,610
能送纸和打印机到我房间吗
Could I have some paper and a typewriter brought up to my room?

347
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:11,499
当然可以 贝耶维小姐
Of course. Miss Bellever?

348
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:12,990
我马上去办
I'll see to it at once.

349
00:21:14,450 --> 00:21:16,979
多美好啊 我们大家齐聚一个屋檐下
How nice. All of us together under the same roof.

350
00:21:16,990 --> 00:21:18,200
没错
Yes.

351
00:21:50,530 --> 00:21:52,600
要是还有什么我能帮上忙的...
Oh, if there's anything more I can do ...

352
00:21:53,290 --> 00:21:55,309
你好好坐着 等下配合入戏就好了
You sit tight and weep like a black sheep.

353
00:21:55,320 --> 00:21:57,199
好吧
Oh. All right.

354
00:21:57,210 --> 00:21:58,270
准备好了吗
All set?

355
00:21:59,330 --> 00:22:01,870
还没到你出场呢
Ooh! That's not your cue!

356
00:22:02,820 --> 00:22:05,940
可我已经出来了 那就开始吧
Well, I'm here now. Let's go on with it. 

357
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:07,670
说话专业点
Spoken like a "pro".

358
00:22:07,760 --> 00:22:09,499
夫人 你忘了你的奎宁水了
Madam, you forgot your tonic.

359
00:22:09,510 --> 00:22:11,340
等一等
Oh, hang on.

360
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:15,789
这活儿一般是我来干的
I normally do this.

361
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:17,940
不好意思 亲爱的 我都忘了
I'm sorry, my darling. I've quite forgotten.

362
00:22:18,570 --> 00:22:20,210
没关系的
Oh! It doesn't matter.

363
00:22:20,211 --> 00:22:21,509
手滑了
Butter fingers.

364
00:22:21,520 --> 00:22:23,639
没事的 刘易斯 真的 小事情
It doesn't matter, Lewis. Really, it's not important.

365
00:22:23,650 --> 00:22:26,120
没关系 乔莉 拿下去 我等会儿再喝
Never mind, Jolly, put it down. I'll take it later.

366
00:22:27,070 --> 00:22:29,498
我想起来了 马普尔小姐
Oh, I wonder, Miss Marple?

367
00:22:29,499 --> 00:22:30,279
什么事
What?

368
00:22:30,290 --> 00:22:32,750
你可不可以...
I wonder, if you wouldn't mind...

369
00:22:32,760 --> 00:22:35,610
我好像没带眼镜
W-well, I don- I don't seem to have my glasses.

370
00:22:35,620 --> 00:22:36,559
你头上不就是吗
On your head?

371
00:22:36,560 --> 00:22:37,999
是的
No. Oh! Yes, it is.

372
00:22:38,010 --> 00:22:39,380
大家都等着呢
Hang on with it!

373
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:56,740
我跋山涉水...
I have travelled far and wide ...

374
00:22:57,620 --> 00:22:58,910
来...
.. to ...

375
00:22:59,860 --> 00:23:02,770
我想应该是"来膜拜你"
I believe it's "to hail you".

376
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:04,099
"来膜拜你..."
"to hail you ..."

377
00:23:04,110 --> 00:23:08,499
来膜拜你...我们部落最伟大的神明
To hail you... to the great gods of our tribe.

378
00:23:08,510 --> 00:23:09,389
饶了我吧
Dear me.

379
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:13,820
他们说 我 伟大的族长
They say that I, Big Chief Running Bear,

380
00:23:14,180 --> 00:23:19,140
必须为了我的所爱 勇敢起来
must brave all ... for the love of my dear.

381
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:21,418
应该是"第三个也是最好的" 刘易斯
"Third and finest", Lewis?

382
00:23:21,419 --> 00:23:21,990
什么
What?

383
00:23:22,120 --> 00:23:23,300
第三个也是最好的
Third and finest.

384
00:23:23,690 --> 00:23:26,240
没错 抱歉 抱歉
Oh! Oh, quite. Sorry. Sorry.

385
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:31,430
为了我第三个也是最好的妻子 夏日雨
My third and finest squaw, Summer Rain.

386
00:23:32,150 --> 00:23:34,150
吉娜 你看起来太可爱了
Oh, Gina, you look lovely!

387
00:23:34,150 --> 00:23:35,150
神哪
Good grief!

388
00:23:49,730 --> 00:23:50,780
我们开始了
Here we go.

389
00:23:52,270 --> 00:23:55,869
她美丽的眼睛 是欢欣的所在
Her beauties eyes most pleasantly framed.

390
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:59,130
太棒了 你太有才了 斯蒂维
Oh, bravo! Most eloquent, Stevie.

391
00:23:59,150 --> 00:24:01,060
艾德加 艾德加
Edgar? Edgar!

392
00:24:01,630 --> 00:24:02,720
坐下
Sit down.

393
00:24:06,490 --> 00:24:07,276
怎么又这样
Oh! Not again! 

394
00:24:07,277 --> 00:24:08,249
电路故障
Wires on the blink.

395
00:24:08,260 --> 00:24:11,260
- 我去检查保险丝 - 好样的 瓦利
- I'll go and check the fuse box. - Good man, Wally.

396
00:24:12,360 --> 00:24:13,600
现在做什么
Well, what now?...

397
00:24:13,910 --> 00:24:16,240
我们可以继续吗 大师
Shall we carry on, maestro, or er ...?

398
00:24:20,070 --> 00:24:22,550
- 当心点 - 看路 艾迪
- Careful! - Steady, Eddie!

399
00:24:23,150 --> 00:24:25,680
- 有什么问题吗 艾德加 - 你还敢问我
- Something wrong, Edgar? - You dare to ask me that?

400
00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:28,619
- 别装得事不关己... - 他有枪
- Calm as you like, when... - He's got a gun!

401
00:24:28,630 --> 00:24:30,109
- 只是个玩具 - 他在演戏
- It's just a toy. - He's playing.

402
00:24:30,120 --> 00:24:32,710
我引起你们的注意了吧 大家都注意了
I've got your attention, everybody? Everybody focused?

403
00:24:33,130 --> 00:24:35,469
别玩了 老兄 今晚的演出够多了
Come on, old man, it's enough theatrics for one night.

404
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:38,240
我要知道真相 我要剩下的人作证
I want the truth! And I want you all by witness.

405
00:24:39,060 --> 00:24:40,657
# 见证人 见证人 # 
By witness, by witness 

406
00:24:40,658 --> 00:24:41,799
别弹了 我是认真的
Be quiet, I'm serious.

407
00:24:41,810 --> 00:24:43,440
斯蒂文 你别捣乱了
Stephen, that really isn't helping!

408
00:24:44,350 --> 00:24:46,070
你吓到我们了
Ok, you're scaring us now.

409
00:24:47,090 --> 00:24:49,409
看看你 可怜巴巴地站在那
Look at you! Just standing, you're pathetic!

410
00:24:49,420 --> 00:24:50,749
谁去把瓦利叫来
Will somebody please, get Wally?

411
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:52,250
围着你的怪念头瞎忙活
Chasing your every whim  your every whim ...

412
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:54,339
他把门给锁了
He's gone and locked the bloody door!

413
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:55,979
把枪放下 艾德加
Put the gun down, Edgar.

414
00:24:55,990 --> 00:24:57,405
点头哈腰 赔笑脸 
A nod here, a smile there, 

415
00:24:57,406 --> 00:24:59,449
"谢谢您 塞罗科尔德先生"
"Thank you, Mr Serrocold!"

416
00:24:59,460 --> 00:25:00,790
艾德加
Edgar!

417
00:25:00,850 --> 00:25:02,349
"要多少糖 塞罗科尔德先生"
"How many sugars, Mr Serrocold?"

418
00:25:02,360 --> 00:25:04,149
"茶够甜了吗 塞罗科尔德先生"
"Tea, sweet enough for you, Mr Serrocold?"

419
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:06,959
- 谁快阻止他 - 别犯傻 他无恶意
- Somebody do something! - Don't be silly. He's harmless.

420
00:25:06,970 --> 00:25:08,279
你怎么知道
How can you say that?

421
00:25:08,290 --> 00:25:09,979
别站在那光说话
Don't you just stand there, with your mouth.

422
00:25:09,990 --> 00:25:11,069
把枪给我
Give me that gun!

423
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:13,500
- 都别动 - 罗森先生
- Nobody move! - Mr. Lawson.

424
00:25:14,560 --> 00:25:17,469
你不觉得进来更舒服些吗
Don't you think that you might be more comfortable inside?

425
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:18,770
都别动
Nobody move!

426
00:25:20,500 --> 00:25:24,599
一直以来都是你窃窃私语 两面三刀
All this time it was you, the whispering, the plotting!

427
00:25:24,610 --> 00:25:28,219
- 艾德加 别发疯了 - 你答应会帮我的
- Edgar, please,this is madness. - You promised to help me!

428
00:25:28,230 --> 00:25:30,610
- 艾德加 够了 - 还要骗我
- Edgar, enough! - More to fool me, hey?

429
00:25:30,650 --> 00:25:33,470
谁都不相信 至少不信你们这帮...
Never trust anyone, at least not in this den of...

430
00:25:33,860 --> 00:25:35,070
瞧你们
Look at you!

431
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:37,629
你们都该送去改造
They ought to send a lot of you out of this precious little fecility

432
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:38,760
看你们怎么...
and see how you...

433
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:41,180
我说了别动
I told you not to move!

434
00:25:41,810 --> 00:25:43,870
- 过来 过来 - 没事了 艾德加
- Come here! Come here! - It's all right, Edgar.

435
00:25:44,230 --> 00:25:45,789
- 跪下 跪下 - 我不会伤害你的
- On your knees! On your knees! - I'm not going to hurt you.

436
00:25:45,800 --> 00:25:46,850
跪下
On your knees!

437
00:25:51,820 --> 00:25:53,030
刘易斯
Lewis!

438
00:25:54,210 --> 00:25:55,460
好疼啊
That hurt!

439
00:25:55,850 --> 00:25:58,030
抓到你了 快放下枪 放下枪
Got you! Come on, drop it, drop it!

440
00:26:00,290 --> 00:26:01,557
好了 闹剧结束了 
There we are. The Show is over! 

441
00:26:01,558 --> 00:26:02,710
艾德加 钥匙拿来
Edgar! The key.

442
00:26:05,920 --> 00:26:07,229
只是小打小闹 是吧
Not exactly a big game, is it?

443
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:09,850
我看他就是欺软怕硬的主
But I suppose you can always try boiling him over to a stop.

444
00:26:10,050 --> 00:26:11,669
- 父亲 - 斯蒂文
- Father? - Stephen!

445
00:26:11,680 --> 00:26:12,779
他来这干嘛
What's he doing here?

446
00:26:12,790 --> 00:26:15,150
刘易斯・塞罗科尔德 很高兴见到你 老兄
Lewis Serrocold? Glad to meet you, old man.

447
00:26:16,180 --> 00:26:19,570
艾德加 下次再这样 直接去找马弗里克医生
Oh, Edgar, whatever next? Search for Dr. Maverick, will you?

448
00:26:19,740 --> 00:26:20,629
谁开枪了
Did I hear gunshots?

449
00:26:20,640 --> 00:26:22,235
你一定是... 
So you must be... 

450
00:26:22,236 --> 00:26:24,470
大首领约翰尼・雷斯塔瑞克
Big Chief Johnny Restarick.

451
00:26:24,560 --> 00:26:27,369
刚从苏豪区和加里克的猎场乘兴而来
Fresh from the happy hunting grounds of Soho and Garrick.

452
00:26:27,380 --> 00:26:31,070
女主人的前任枕边人
And former tenant of the great white bed.

453
00:26:31,150 --> 00:26:34,320
能来点润喉的吗 老兄
Any chance of something moist in a glass, old man?

454
00:26:34,990 --> 00:26:35,960
当然
Why not?

455
00:26:36,350 --> 00:26:40,880
瞧你 我的波提切利天使
Ha! Look at you, my Botticelli angel!

456
00:26:42,900 --> 00:26:44,289
我们要报警
We have to call the police.

457
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:46,960
没必要 艾德加也平静下来了
Oh! There's no need to fuss. Edgar is quite himself again.

458
00:26:47,040 --> 00:26:48,840
刘易斯也没事 是吧 亲爱的
And Lewis is fine. Aren't you, darling?

459
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:51,260
我说的不是塞罗科尔德先生
It wasn't Mr. Serrocold I was thinking of.

460
00:27:11,800 --> 00:27:16,040
他总是很注重仪表
He was always so precise about his appearance.

461
00:27:23,930 --> 00:27:25,200
我很抱歉
I'm so sorry.

462
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:29,740
谁会如此狠毒
How could anyone do such a thing?

463
00:27:31,690 --> 00:27:34,499
抱歉 卡莉・路易斯 但你知道
Forgive me, Carrie Louise, but had you any idea that

464
00:27:34,510 --> 00:27:37,760
今晚你前夫会来吗
your former husband was coming to Stonygates tonight?

465
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:39,490
约翰尼
Johnny?

466
00:27:40,320 --> 00:27:41,760
是的 你怎么知道
Yes. How did you know?

467
00:27:42,300 --> 00:27:44,770
早些 亲爱的 我们在温室旁时
Earlier, dear, when we were near the glasshouse,

468
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:47,319
你试图告诉我你的烦恼
you tried to tell me what was troubling you.

469
00:27:47,330 --> 00:27:48,420
是这样的...
Yes, you see...

470
00:27:50,350 --> 00:27:52,710
约翰尼总是像追求者一样
..Johnny kept writing me these long letters,

471
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:55,010
给我写情书
like some supplicant at the gate,

472
00:27:55,330 --> 00:27:57,830
如果我拒绝他 他就没完
threatening to end it all, if I turned him away.

473
00:27:58,540 --> 00:28:00,480
- 你给过他希望吗 - 绝没有
- And you gave him hope? - Never!

474
00:28:01,420 --> 00:28:03,860
但天知道刘易斯会怎么想
Though heaven knows what Lewis will make of it.

475
00:28:04,070 --> 00:28:06,349
每当他在报纸上看到约翰尼的名字
He gets into the most deadful huff

476
00:28:06,360 --> 00:28:08,360
他都会吃干醋
if he so much sees Johnny's name in the newspaper.

477
00:28:14,670 --> 00:28:17,990
- 塞罗科尔德夫人 - 请进
- Mrs. Serrocold? - Do come in.

478
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:27,150
克里探长 夫人 这是我的助理莱克警官
Inspetor Curry, ma'm. My assistent, sargeant Lake.

479
00:28:27,860 --> 00:28:30,510
- 死者是你的继子吧 - 是的
- Your stepson, I gather. - That's right.

480
00:28:31,150 --> 00:28:32,829
是我已故第一任丈夫的儿子
About my late first husband.

481
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:36,660
这么晚了还发生这可怕的噩耗
Dreadful shock, a bit of a late night, I imagine.

482
00:28:37,180 --> 00:28:40,230
简・马普尔 塞罗科尔德夫人的朋友
Jane Marple. Friend of Mrs. Serrocold.

483
00:28:41,220 --> 00:28:43,500
给夫人搬个椅子来 警官
Chair for the lady, Sargeant.

484
00:28:51,210 --> 00:28:55,470
先讲我了解到的情况
So... let's see if I got this straight.

485
00:28:57,180 --> 00:28:59,470
死者今天到达来找你丈夫 
The deceased arrived today 

486
00:28:59,471 --> 00:29:01,570
刘易斯・塞罗科尔德先生
on a pressing matter of business

487
00:29:01,580 --> 00:29:04,070
商讨生意上的要紧事
with your husband, Mr. Lewis Serrocold.

488
00:29:05,210 --> 00:29:09,000
死者用过少许晚餐后 回房休息
The deceased then retired to his room after a light supper,

489
00:29:09,590 --> 00:29:12,630
然后背部被刺...
where he was stabbed in the back...

490
00:29:13,150 --> 00:29:15,469
与此同时 其他人都被锁在楼下客厅
..while the rest of the company were busy downstairs,locked

491
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:20,469
看戏剧表演 其间艾德加・罗森先生
in the drawing room, for a theatrical performance that went a riot

492
00:29:20,480 --> 00:29:24,620
出来闹过事
on account of a Mr... Edgar Lawson.

493
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:25,779
是这样的
That's correct.

494
00:29:25,790 --> 00:29:30,019
那个你无需担心 探长先生 是一段小插曲
Nothing to concern you there, inspector. A momentary aberration.

495
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:32,760
艾德加・罗森是你这里的犯人之一吗
One of your convicts, hey, this Edgar Lawson?

496
00:29:32,930 --> 00:29:35,200
- 什么意思 - 他是什么人
- What of it? - What's he in for?

497
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:36,410
明白了
Oh, I see.

498
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:39,400
艾德加只是幻想
Edgar rather pressed his atention 

499
00:29:39,401 --> 00:29:42,280
他和社会名流有关系
on one or two pillars of

500
00:29:42,680 --> 00:29:46,719
丘吉尔先生 蒙哥马利子爵等等 
society. Mr. Churchill... Viscount Montgomery, and so on...

501
00:29:46,730 --> 00:29:50,060
他和我们在一起两年了 已经有了很大的进步
He's been with us two years. He's made great strides.

502
00:29:50,450 --> 00:29:51,869
他可以进入枪械室吗
And he had access to the gun room?

503
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:54,415
艾德加是我丈夫的私人助理 
Edgar is my husband's personal secretary. 

504
00:29:54,416 --> 00:29:55,430
我明白了
I see.

505
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:58,959
我们经常会雇佣劳教人员
From time to time, we employ individuals from the facility.

506
00:29:58,970 --> 00:30:01,470
承担更多的责任使他们受益
Those who'd benefict from added responsability.

507
00:30:01,520 --> 00:30:04,210
罗森先生现在在哪
Where is he now, this Mr. Lawson?

508
00:30:04,260 --> 00:30:08,060
睡了 马弗里克医生给他打了镇定剂
Asleep. Dr. Maverick sedated him.

509
00:30:08,230 --> 00:30:11,710
- 其他犯人呢 - 在安全的宵禁
- And were the other convicts? - Safely under curfew.

510
00:30:12,580 --> 00:30:17,199
庄园的所有大门 下午五点会准时锁上
All the gates of the property are locked at 05:00PM sharp.

511
00:30:17,210 --> 00:30:18,190
当然
Of course.

512
00:30:21,650 --> 00:30:25,360
这个...就是杀人凶器了
This er... would be the murder weapon, then.

513
00:30:27,330 --> 00:30:28,770
像是军用的
Military flavour.

514
00:30:28,860 --> 00:30:29,739
认识吗
Familiar at all?

515
00:30:29,750 --> 00:30:34,480
它是...曾是瓦利・哈德先生的
It belonged... belongs to a Mr. Wally Hudd.

