Footsteps. And then the gun.

682
00:39:01,970 --> 00:39:02,909
我当时便想
And I thought to myself: now that's

683
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:06,840
这样的效果完全可以用在莱姆豪斯之夜
exactly the effect that I want for my Limehouse Nights.

684
00:39:07,690 --> 00:39:10,010
- 我的芭蕾舞剧 - 脚步声吗
- My ballet? - Footsteps?

685
00:39:10,720 --> 00:39:14,170
- 哪边来的 - 分辨不出来 老伙计
- Where from? - Impossible to say, old man.

686
00:39:14,520 --> 00:39:18,839
所以你是穿过花园走到了落地窗前
So, you crossed the garden to the french windows.

687
00:39:18,850 --> 00:39:22,530
是啊 好奇要去看看
Yeah. Yes. Well, fancied to a closer look.

688
00:39:23,470 --> 00:39:24,860
有什么问题吗
Anything wrong with that?

689
00:39:41,720 --> 00:39:43,210
我怪我自己
I blame myself.

690
00:39:43,950 --> 00:39:45,000
克里斯提安死了 
Christian dead, 

691
00:39:45,001 --> 00:39:46,969
现在又是吉娜她那年轻的美国小伙
and now Gina's young american.

692
00:39:46,980 --> 00:39:49,249
你觉得瓦利可能是杀人犯吗
You think Wally might have committed the murder?

693
00:39:49,260 --> 00:39:50,740
我也不知道
I don't know what to think.

694
00:39:51,050 --> 00:39:52,410
但有时候我很疑惑
But sometimes I wonder.

695
00:39:53,420 --> 00:39:54,899
她如此匆忙地结婚
The way she rushed into the marriage,

696
00:39:54,910 --> 00:39:57,410
是不是为了得到母亲的注意
was it for want of a mother's affection?

697
00:39:59,540 --> 00:40:01,589
我真不应该花这么多时间在工作上
If I'd been less consumed with my own work.

698
00:40:01,600 --> 00:40:03,049
而是花更多的时间和精力在她身上
If I'd given more time, or more energy.

699
00:40:03,060 --> 00:40:07,230
小孩都需要被关怀 被爱护 不是吗
A child needs to feel cherished in the nursery, doesn't she?

700
00:40:07,430 --> 00:40:09,830
不然她便一直不知道自己存在的意义
Or she'll never come to know her own value.

701
00:40:10,420 --> 00:40:13,370
更何况 还是领养的小孩
Above all, an adopted child.

702
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:21,890
什么声音
What was that?

703
00:40:22,510 --> 00:40:23,830
不 看
Oh, no, look!

704
00:40:27,070 --> 00:40:28,850
停下来 警察
Stop! Police!

705
00:40:29,050 --> 00:40:30,140
停下来
Stop!

706
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:34,370
警察
Police!

707
00:41:06,410 --> 00:41:07,610
瓦利 
Wally!

708
00:41:10,910 --> 00:41:13,320
瓦利
Oh! Oh, Wally!

709
00:41:13,750 --> 00:41:15,020
他还有呼吸吗
Is he breathing?

710
00:41:16,630 --> 00:41:17,820
我们到了吗
Are we there?

711
00:41:19,700 --> 00:41:22,419
这真是荒谬 你们应该立刻叫我过来
This is monstrous! I should have been summoned at once!

712
00:41:22,430 --> 00:41:24,189
我是受托人 我有权利
I am a Trustee. I have rights.

713
00:41:24,200 --> 00:41:26,099
如果有人想要杀我的姐姐...
And if someone is trying to kill my sister ...

714
00:41:26,110 --> 00:41:29,199
恐怕这不是"如果" 我刚收到了确认的电报
No "if" about that, I'm affraid. I just received a telegram confirming

715
00:41:29,210 --> 00:41:31,799
塞罗科尔德夫人的药中含有砒霜
the presence of arsenic in Mrs. Serrocold's bottle of tonic.

716
00:41:31,810 --> 00:41:33,387
那我们应该立刻告诉她 
Then we must tell her at once! 

717
00:41:33,388 --> 00:41:34,480
我的老天 鲁思
For pete's sake, Ruth!

718
00:41:34,560 --> 00:41:36,149
先等到明天我们做好准备 以防万一好吗
Keep your powder dry until the morning, will ya?

719
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:38,679
真是奇怪
Oh, how perfectly quaint!

720
00:41:38,690 --> 00:41:40,780
难怪你们国家会输掉整个王国
No wonder you people have lost the Empire.

721
00:41:40,790 --> 00:41:42,568
杀人犯仍在逍遥法外 
There's a killer on the loose! 

722
00:41:42,569 --> 00:41:44,050
你以为我不知道吗
You think I don't know that?

723
00:41:44,210 --> 00:41:45,259
每次她拿起勺子送到嘴边
You think I don't hold my breath

724
00:41:45,270 --> 00:41:47,240
我都心惊胆战的
every time she lifts a spoon to her lips?

725
00:41:47,690 --> 00:41:50,429
我也在尽最大的努力保护我的妻子
I'm trying to protect my wife as lovingly as I can.

726
00:41:50,440 --> 00:41:53,290
你为她太小题大做了 一直都是这样
You're making too much fuss of her. You always have.

727
00:41:58,500 --> 00:42:00,269
哈德先生情况怎么样了
How is Mr. Hudd fairing?

728
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:03,060
我们随时都可以把他带走 女士
Oh, we'll have him off your in no time, ma'am

729
00:42:03,490 --> 00:42:05,960
只要等他可以移动就好
just as soon as he's fit to move.

730
00:42:31,510 --> 00:42:33,340
我怎么知道他在想什么
How would I know what he's been up to?

731
00:42:33,900 --> 00:42:35,239
他要做什么 我怎么知道
How would I know the first thing about him?

732
00:42:35,250 --> 00:42:36,890
我只是他的妻子
I'm only his wife, after all!

733
00:42:38,040 --> 00:42:40,110
对不起 房间很乱
Sorry. Such mess.

734
00:42:40,340 --> 00:42:41,870
在抽屉某处找到的
Found this in a drawer, somewhere.

735
00:42:41,910 --> 00:42:45,180
虽然我没有仔细想 但看起来像是预谋好的
It's the er... air of contriver, as I don't care for.

736
00:42:45,200 --> 00:42:46,680
什么
What?

737
00:42:47,340 --> 00:42:50,820
我只是在想 这一切都那么巧合
Well, I was just thinking how convenient it all was,

738
00:42:51,330 --> 00:42:55,510
我们安全地被困在了客厅
there we were in the drawing room, safely under locking key,

739
00:42:55,830 --> 00:42:57,720
而碰巧这时候...
preciselly the moment when ...

740
00:42:57,800 --> 00:42:59,113
我明白你的意思 
I get it your point. 

741
00:42:59,114 --> 00:43:01,740
但如果没有别的地方可以出去...
But if there was no other way out ...

742
00:43:02,490 --> 00:43:04,910
瓦利 不
Wally! No!

743
00:43:06,130 --> 00:43:08,510
吉娜 吉娜
Gina? Gina!

744
00:43:10,190 --> 00:43:12,719
你们不能带走他 不能带走他
Don't you dare, gents! Don't you dare!

745
00:43:12,730 --> 00:43:13,960
放开他
Get away from them!

746
00:43:14,560 --> 00:43:16,479
放开 我不会让你们带走他的
Get away! I won't let you ...

747
00:43:16,490 --> 00:43:17,619
你们不能带走他
You can't take him away.

748
00:43:17,630 --> 00:43:19,830
我有很重要的事要告诉探长
I've got something very important to tell the Inspector!

749
00:43:23,270 --> 00:43:25,340
这真是新鲜事 
What fresh air is this, hey?

750
00:43:25,740 --> 00:43:28,150
给
Here, take. 

751
00:43:28,310 --> 00:43:30,669
- 别闹 别闹 吉娜 - 放开
- Please, please, Gina! - Let go!

752
00:43:30,680 --> 00:43:35,509
- 放开他 - 别闹了 吉娜
- Come! Leave him! - Gina, please!

753
00:43:35,520 --> 00:43:37,339
冷静点 你这是在帮倒忙
Calm down, please. This isn't helping at all.

754
00:43:37,350 --> 00:43:39,540
- 他什么都没做 - 先进来
- He hasn't done anything! - Come inside.

755
00:43:41,310 --> 00:43:43,930
好了 年轻的小姐 你想要给我们看什么
Now, young lady, what was it you wanted to show us?

756
00:43:44,100 --> 00:43:45,740
我们任何一个人都能离开这房间
Anyone of us could have left this room 

757
00:43:45,741 --> 00:43:47,030
去杀那可怜的克里斯提安
to murder poor Christian.

758
00:43:49,690 --> 00:43:50,920
那儿 看到了吗
There, you see?

759
00:43:55,620 --> 00:43:58,510
进吧 莱克警官 进来吧
Come on, sargeant Lake. Come on.

760
00:43:59,260 --> 00:44:00,390
去吧
Go on.

761
00:44:02,940 --> 00:44:04,460
这边来 探长先生
This way, Inspector.

762
00:44:11,090 --> 00:44:12,140
来
Come.

763
00:44:12,700 --> 00:44:14,020
她去哪儿了
Where does she go?

764
00:44:26,700 --> 00:44:28,370
先生 有火柴
Sir, look. Matches.

765
00:44:28,890 --> 00:44:30,950
- 最近的吗 - 应该是的
- Recents? - I should say.

766
00:44:32,150 --> 00:44:33,630
很奇怪的味道
Interesting smell.

767
00:44:33,650 --> 00:44:35,680
- 柴油吗 - 有可能
- Diesel? - Possibly.

768
00:44:35,960 --> 00:44:37,298
看到了吗 探长先生 
So, you see, Inspector, 

769
00:44:37,299 --> 00:44:38,770
我们任何一个人都有嫌疑
any of us could have done it.

770
00:44:38,770 --> 00:44:41,959
这真是荒谬 罗森先生一开始表演
That's absurd. Once Mr. Lawson started firing,

771
00:44:41,970 --> 00:44:43,299
我们全都在原地不动
we were all frozen to the spot.

772
00:44:43,310 --> 00:44:44,780
没有人动过吗
Nobody moved?

773
00:44:45,260 --> 00:44:48,580
哈德先生离开的期间 所有人都在场吗
Everyone present and correct throughout Mr. Hudd's absence?

774
00:44:51,450 --> 00:44:54,040
- 我要你们成为我的见证人 - 是的
- And I want all of you to be my witnesses. - Absolutely.

775
00:44:54,750 --> 00:44:56,660
但那时候停电了
But the lights were out.

776
00:44:58,190 --> 00:44:59,820
那我也看见了
I know what I saw.

777
00:44:59,910 --> 00:45:01,270
斯蒂文吗
Stephen?

778
00:45:01,870 --> 00:45:04,009
他在弹琴 我叫他停下来
He was lurking at the piano. I told him not.

779
00:45:04,020 --> 00:45:05,740
斯蒂文 你这是在帮倒忙
Stephen, that really isn't helping.

780
00:45:05,760 --> 00:45:08,280
不是 斯蒂文跑去帮忙了
No, no. Stephen went for help.

781
00:45:08,290 --> 00:45:10,079
这些日子 帮你写信
All these weeks writing your letters.

782
00:45:10,090 --> 00:45:12,000
他出去时把门锁了
He's gone and locked the bloody door!

783
00:45:12,250 --> 00:45:14,980
那...他在那儿之后去哪儿了
And er ... where did he go after that?

784
00:45:15,170 --> 00:45:16,800
我也不清楚
I couldn't honestly say.

785
00:45:17,710 --> 00:45:19,260
那年轻的哈德夫人呢
And young Mrs. Hudd?

786
00:45:19,600 --> 00:45:20,590
吉娜吗
Gina?

787
00:45:22,070 --> 00:45:24,160
她和我一起 就在其他人身后
She was with me, just behind the others.

788
00:45:28,070 --> 00:45:30,110
你确定吗
You quite certain of that fact?

789
00:45:30,350 --> 00:45:34,140
你这一问...
Well, now that you press me ...

790
00:45:35,080 --> 00:45:37,390
她从窗户那边走过来
.. She came away from the window ...

791
00:45:37,470 --> 00:45:39,180
请把瓦利叫过来
Will somebody, please, get Wally?

792
00:45:39,460 --> 00:45:41,429
穿着那可笑的衣服
.. in that preposterous outfit,

793
00:45:41,440 --> 00:45:42,720
可那之后...
but then ...

794
00:45:45,650 --> 00:45:47,419
你是在怀疑我妹妹...
You don't think my sister could ...

795
00:45:47,430 --> 00:45:50,720
我们目前还没有任何结论
Now, we are not jumping to any conclusions.

796
00:45:50,920 --> 00:45:54,359
她这人一直都非常轻浮 反复无常 
Well, she's always been flighty. Unpredictable, volatile.

797
00:45:54,370 --> 00:45:57,960
自从她来了这里以后 便一直粘着妈妈
And she's sticking to mamma like fly-paper since the moment she got here.

798
00:46:00,040 --> 00:46:01,370
米尔德里德吗
What, Mildred?

799
00:46:04,680 --> 00:46:06,600
她撞倒了那张小桌子
Well, she knocked in that little table.

800
00:46:06,760 --> 00:46:08,770
那之后 我就不知道她去哪儿了
After that, I don't know where's she gone to.

801
00:46:09,840 --> 00:46:12,140
那请问 探长先生
So, now, Inspector

802
00:46:13,230 --> 00:46:16,280
你不会再逮捕瓦利了吧
you're not really going to arrest my Wally, are you?

803
00:46:33,920 --> 00:46:35,250
你在这儿做什么
What are you doing out here?

804
00:46:47,820 --> 00:46:49,110
闻到了吗
Smell that?

805
00:46:52,940 --> 00:46:54,260
大红木
Giant red-wood.

806
00:46:59,010 --> 00:47:00,570
美国的味道
Smells of America.

807
00:47:04,020 --> 00:47:07,430
这宝贝是我在这儿唯一能信任的东西了
This baby is about the last thing in this damn place I can count in.

808
00:47:10,440 --> 00:47:12,040
别这么伤感
Don't be so melodramatic

809
00:47:12,710 --> 00:47:16,540
还有 这"宝贝"是巨杉 不是红木
anyway, this "baby" is a Wellingtonia, not redwood.

810
00:47:19,910 --> 00:47:23,340
- 没有区别 - 瓦利
- Makes no difference. - Wally.

811
00:47:26,710 --> 00:47:30,150
瓦利 你骑着自行车要去哪里
Wally, where were you going in that bicycle?

812
00:47:34,070 --> 00:47:35,400
留下我怎么办
What about me?

813
00:48:32,130 --> 00:48:35,610
- 亲爱的 你在做什么 - 干活
- Darling, what're you doing? - Keeping busy.

814
00:48:38,980 --> 00:48:41,339
他又蛮不讲理了吗
Oh, has he been a brut again?

815
00:48:41,350 --> 00:48:43,500
- 他没有蛮不讲理 - 当然啦
- He's not a brut. - Of course not.

816
00:48:43,620 --> 00:48:45,289
但他那样一个人 在你这样的姑娘面前
But a chap like that, And a gal like you,

817
00:48:45,300 --> 00:48:47,189
他怎么会知道你想要什么
he doesn't know what makes you tick.

818
00:48:47,200 --> 00:48:50,529
- 他怎么知道 - 我想要什么
- How could he? - What makes me tick?

819
00:48:50,540 --> 00:48:52,020
镇里的公寓
A flat in town.

820
00:48:52,580 --> 00:48:54,579
装满漂亮衣服的衣柜
A wardrobe heaving with pretty clothes.

821
00:48:54,590 --> 00:48:57,519
和一个爱干净的大眼情人
And a cow-eyed lover who doesn't leave crums in the bed.

822
00:48:57,530 --> 00:48:58,930
没错吧
Am I right?

823
00:49:00,720 --> 00:49:02,270
你一点都不了解我 
You don't know the first thing about me. 

824
00:49:02,271 --> 00:49:03,680
我了解得足够多了
I know all I need.

825
00:49:04,550 --> 00:49:06,859
总有一天 我会和克罗伊斯君王一样富有
One day, I'm gonna be as rich as Croesus.

826
00:49:06,870 --> 00:49:08,310
只要我的话剧上演
As soon as I receive my play off.

827
00:49:09,100 --> 00:49:13,630
而你 亲爱的 将会成为克罗伊斯皇后
And you, my dear, you shall be as rich as Mrs. Croesus.

828
00:49:16,280 --> 00:49:17,610
嫁给我
Marry me.

829
00:49:18,370 --> 00:49:19,460
傻瓜
Idiot!

830
00:49:19,720 --> 00:49:21,900
你不是喜欢男人围着你转吗
You like to having men mooning after you, don't you?

831
00:49:22,770 --> 00:49:24,709
是的 很残忍吧
Yes. Is it very cruel?

832
00:49:24,720 --> 00:49:26,670
太残忍了
Yes. Terribly.

833
00:49:27,320 --> 00:49:28,410
但是
Still...

834
00:49:29,750 --> 00:49:32,370
用不了几年 我就没那魔力了
..in a few years the magic will soon wear off

835
00:49:34,370 --> 00:49:36,790
没人会再关注我了
and no-one will look at me ever again.

836
00:49:38,800 --> 00:49:41,740
所有人 甚至你
And everyone, even you ...

837
00:49:43,150 --> 00:49:45,770
都会看到我有多堕落
.. will see how truly rotten how really am.

838
00:49:52,230 --> 00:49:53,560
斯蒂文
Stephen!

839
00:49:56,180 --> 00:49:57,440
你好 蜜儿
Hello, Mil.

840
00:49:58,540 --> 00:49:59,980
你们怎么能
How could you?

841
00:50:01,240 --> 00:50:02,739
不过我倒不惊讶
I don't know why I'm surprised.

842
00:50:02,750 --> 00:50:05,479
什么事都跟吉娜有关 跟谁都有一腿
Anything goes with Gina. Or anyone.

843
00:50:05,490 --> 00:50:06,860
请别说出去
Please, don't say anything.

844
00:50:07,570 --> 00:50:09,009
你不会说的吧 蜜儿
You won't say anything, will you, Mil?

845
00:50:09,020 --> 00:50:11,879
- 你们选的时间恶心到我了 - 时间
- It's the timing that sickens me. - Timing?

846
00:50:11,890 --> 00:50:14,190
- 妈妈被人下毒了 - 什么
- Mother being poisoned. - What?

847
00:50:14,280 --> 00:50:16,620
没听说吗
Ha, didn't you hear?

848
00:50:16,950 --> 00:50:19,649
- 很明显是砒霜 - 别说了 蜜儿
- With arsenic, aparently. - Give it a rest, Mil.

849
00:50:19,660 --> 00:50:24,350
震惊了吧
Mm... mark the air of tragic surprise.

850
00:50:24,670 --> 00:50:27,210
别装无辜 小妞
Don't come with innocent with me, young lady.

851
00:50:28,670 --> 00:50:33,170
我说过 血统
As I said, blood, well... out.

852
00:50:40,930 --> 00:50:44,250
毒死塞罗科尔德太太 谁受益最大呢
Who had most to gain from the poisoning of Mrs. Serrocold?

853
00:50:44,260 --> 00:50:46,460
如果我妻子死了
In the event of my wife's death,

854
00:50:46,810 --> 00:50:49,789
房产是平分给两个女儿的
the estate is to be divided equally between our daughters,

855
00:50:49,800 --> 00:50:51,120
吉娜和米尔德里德
Gina and Mildred.

856
00:50:51,470 --> 00:50:54,549
还有一万美元给她的闺蜜
And, in addition $10.000 to her companion..

857
00:50:54,560 --> 00:50:55,879
贝耶维小姐
Miss Bellever?

858
00:50:55,890 --> 00:50:59,150
还有一万美元给小斯蒂文
