If it wasn't you ...

1389
01:21:37,140 --> 01:21:38,710
艾德加・罗森
Edgar Lawson!

1390
01:21:39,050 --> 01:21:40,450
父亲
Father?

1391
01:21:41,250 --> 01:21:42,720
- 艾德加 - 警官快去
- Edgar! - Sargeant!

1392
01:21:45,800 --> 01:21:47,890
- 艾德加 - 孩子
- Edgar! - Son!

1393
01:22:12,960 --> 01:22:14,160
艾德加
Edgar!

1394
01:22:36,060 --> 01:22:38,260
快点 快
Come on! quick!

1395
01:22:40,080 --> 01:22:41,680
伙计们 赶紧
Hurry up, lads!

1396
01:22:48,210 --> 01:22:49,530
快
Quick!

1397
01:23:01,560 --> 01:23:02,950
继续找
Keep looking!

1398
01:23:30,120 --> 01:23:33,320
- 你知道艾德加的事情吗 - 我在想
- Did you know? - I wondered.

1399
01:23:34,000 --> 01:23:35,879
