the quest for a missing father. I. .. I'm so sorry.

1404
01:23:50,170 --> 01:23:52,510
刘易斯 为什么他不直接告诉我呢
Oh, Lewis. Why didn't he just tell me?

1405
01:23:53,050 --> 01:23:55,499
