It's part of a hidden door. Here, let me show you.

1413
01:24:25,020 --> 01:24:27,150
- 亲爱的 帮我一下 - 当然
- Oh, help me, darling. - Of course.

1414
01:24:33,260 --> 01:24:34,690
真是聪明
So clever.

1415
01:24:37,870 --> 01:24:40,449
