and, apparently, the pilot refuses to wait.

1418
01:24:44,730 --> 01:24:45,409
当然
Of course.

1419
01:24:45,420 --> 01:24:47,830
你确定不改主意了吗
Are you sure you won't change your mind?

1420
01:24:47,910 --> 01:24:50,179
这个时候的曼哈顿真的很棒
Manhattan is fabulous at this time of the year.

1421
01:24:50,190 --> 01:24:51,880
