Where've you been?

1427
01:25:34,990 --> 01:25:36,510
你在这做什么
What're you doing here?

1428
01:25:37,290 --> 01:25:38,530
你错了
You're wrong.

1429
01:25:40,520 --> 01:25:41,760
我查了一下
I looked it up.

1430
