I just can't believe you still want me.

1445
01:26:45,560 --> 01:26:46,840
你还没明白吗
Don't you get it?

1446
01:26:47,730 --> 01:26:49,410
我从来没有... 
There was never...

1447
01:26:49,411 --> 01:26:51,650
从来没有哪一刻我不...
